import { Box, Container, Typography, Grid, Card, CardMedia, CardContent, Button } from '@mui/material';
import { DirectionsCar, LocalGasStation, Speed, CalendarToday } from '@mui/icons-material';

function Inventory() {
  const carImages = [
    'bmw1.jpg',
    'bmw2.jpg',
    'bmw3.jpg',
    'bmw4.jpg'
  ];

  return (
    <Box sx={{ py: 8, bgcolor: '#171717', minHeight: '100vh', color: 'white' }}>
      <Container maxWidth="lg">
        <Typography variant="h2" sx={{ mb: 4, fontWeight: 700 }}>
          Available Vehicles
        </Typography>

        {/* Car Details Section */}
        <Card sx={{ bgcolor: '#262626', mb: 6 }}>
          <Grid container>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <CardMedia
                component="img"
                height="400"
                image={carImages[0]}
                alt="BMW 1 Series"
                sx={{ 
                  objectFit: 'cover',
                  width: '100%'
                }}
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
              <CardContent sx={{ p: 4, color: 'white' }}>
                <Typography variant="h3" gutterBottom sx={{ fontWeight: 700 }}>
                  BMW 1 Series 116i (2012)
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ color: '#dc2626', mb: 3 }}>
                  £8,995
                </Typography>

                {/* Specifications */}
                <Grid container spacing={2} sx={{ mb: 3 }}>
                  <Grid item xs={6} sm={3}>
                    <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                      <DirectionsCar sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#dc2626', mb: 1 }} />
                      <Typography variant="body2">Mileage</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="h6">75,000</Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={6} sm={3}>
                    <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                      <LocalGasStation sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#dc2626', mb: 1 }} />
                      <Typography variant="body2">Fuel</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="h6">Petrol</Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={6} sm={3}>
                    <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                      <Speed sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#dc2626', mb: 1 }} />
                      <Typography variant="body2">Engine</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="h6">1.6L</Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item xs={6} sm={3}>
                    <Box sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                      <CalendarToday sx={{ fontSize: 40, color: '#dc2626', mb: 1 }} />
                      <Typography variant="body2">Year</Typography>
                      <Typography variant="h6">2012</Typography>
                    </Box>
                  </Grid>
                </Grid>

                <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{ mt: 3 }}>
                  Features:
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body1" paragraph>
                  • Air Conditioning
                  • Electric Windows
                  • Bluetooth Connectivity
                  • Parking Sensors
                  • Alloy Wheels
                  • Full Service History
                </Typography>

                <Button 
                  variant="contained"
                  size="large"
                  sx={{ 
                    bgcolor: '#dc2626',
                    '&:hover': {
                      bgcolor: '#b91c1c'
                    },
                    mt: 2
                  }}
                >
                  Enquire Now
                </Button>
              </CardContent>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Card>

        {/* Gallery Section */}
        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ mb: 3, fontWeight: 700 }}>
          Gallery
        </Typography>
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          {carImages.map((image, index) => (
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={index}>
              <Card 
                sx={{ 
                  bgcolor: '#262626',
                  transition: '0.3s',
                  '&:hover': {
                    transform: 'scale(1.02)'
                  }
                }}
              >
                <CardMedia
                  component="img"
                  height="250"
                  image={image}
                  alt={`BMW 1 Series Image ${index + 1}`}
                  sx={{ 
                    objectFit: 'cover',
                    width: '100%'
                  }}
                />
              </Card>
            </Grid>
          ))}
        </Grid>
      </Container>
    </Box>
  );
}

export default Inventory;
